{"tid":150731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"CNN主持人訪食人族　吃人腦直呼「好脆」","createTime":"2017-03-10T09:31:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-12T19:45:11.000Z","uid":1886,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"982dec77114ae17f5114c6211af7c9cfc50e3ad8","tid":150731,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T09:31:48.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>CNN主持人訪食人族　吃人腦直呼「好脆」<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170310/1073102/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170310%2F1073102%2F&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTYy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=d53894c5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170310/1073102/</a></strong></span></div><br />\n<br />\n美國《CNN》近日製播一個節目，邀請宗教學者阿斯蘭(Reza Aslan)擔任主持人，探訪印度食人族教派「Aghori」。阿斯蘭也入境隨俗吃人腦，但拍攝過程中一度被食人族代表丟大便，並威脅他：「要把你的頭割下來。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170310/640_9f93157fae35adb0f2c2d3b985093b74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170310%2F640_9f93157fae35adb0f2c2d3b985093b74.jpg&h=71086961&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這名Aghori教徒威脅阿斯蘭要把他的頭割下來。翻自《鏡報》<br />\n<br />\n阿斯蘭在節目中探訪Aghori教派，他在恆河沐浴後，Aghori信徒在他身上抹骨灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，代表淨化，並用人體顱骨盛酒給他喝，更將人腦烤熟後給阿斯蘭吃，阿斯蘭事後在自家的臉書中寫道：「吃人腦的味道如何？像木炭，烤得很酥脆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。」阿斯蘭還目睹信徒飲用自己的尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，隨後信徒口出狂言：「如果你說太多話，我就要把你的頭割下來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。」隨後信徒當場大便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，並把糞便丟向阿斯蘭和攝影團隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170310/640_4e96b1220f71c9059e3a4d4fe9388502.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170310%2F640_4e96b1220f71c9059e3a4d4fe9388502.jpg&h=be5d7ae2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n宗教學者阿斯蘭擔任CNN主持人訪食人族，被塗抹骨灰代表淨化。翻自《鏡報》<br />\n<br />\nAghori教徒相信人體不受任何事物污染，也拒絕接受印度的種姓制度。但此節目播出後，立刻引起美國印度教徒強烈不滿，指CNN刻意醜化印度教，因為有很多印度裔美國人在這次大選期間挺總統川普，而阿斯蘭在推特上辯護稱：「這是關於Aghori的節目，不是印度教。」"},{"pid":"a59e0b013a62f8382ea5c259c7b356774da37622","tid":150731,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T09:34:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170309/large/1489049794_81ea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170309%2Flarge%2F1489049794_81ea.jpg&h=ea33291a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170309/large/1489049795_b84e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170309%2Flarge%2F1489049795_b84e.jpg&h=b0c2053a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170309/large/1489049796_2d85.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170309%2Flarge%2F1489049796_2d85.jpg&h=658cd2c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fa9ceabd1cc785dadfa99e9a1a00862fb6b3cfbe","tid":150731,"uid":29273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T09:36:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85cf45c42afae0ba3c4fed678cf81b27943dc39d","tid":150731,"uid":16372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T09:37:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f83e84f963122a393343e48091815907886ecc6","tid":150731,"uid":21896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime